lenders.name: Raman Vishwanathan
lenders.loan_because:
No better way to help people in need than to lend them the money -- by the people, for the people.
With a loan I am assured to some degree that the money would be used directly and efficiently by someone in need. Further, a loan instills a sense of self-respect in the borrower compared to charity. Hopefully some day, when they are in a position to aid someone in need, that will be a direct measure of success.
Programs like this have the capacity to make the world a better place for future generations.
